title: #92Noon! 9a Hour 4/22 - What Happened to the Howl?
description: PA & Charch make up the Friday Feast, but the first hour is all about the ridiculous meltdown by the Wolves at Target Center last night. Grizzlies vox Eric Hasseltine is in studio for most of the hour as we recap that hideous loss by the Howl.
